# NOSC/KHOA OpenAPI service key.
# Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key. The VITE_ prefix is required for
# Vite to expose it to the browser code (import.meta.env.VITE_NOSC_SERVICE_KEY).
# Get a key at https://www.nosc.go.kr/openapi/actionOpenApiIssue.do
#
# SECURITY: a key in client-side env is bundled into the JS and visible to
# anyone using the app. Keep `.env` out of git (it is gitignored) and treat the
# key as low-trust. For a public deployment, proxy the API through a backend
# that holds the key instead.
VITE_NOSC_SERVICE_KEY=
